  h1 Make your first call now!
    br
    br
    h3 <strong>Step 0</strong>: Check out <a href='https://docs.google.com/document/d/14lWdOdMRJVfP8VPouz47SOOtLXlGOzxxcmNwVWDyM6s/edit?usp=drivesdk' target='_blank'>this guide</a> to learn about phone banking and why this work is important to Bernie. For a more detailed walkthrough, checkout the Official <a href='https://www.berniesanders.com/phonebank'>phonebanking page</a>. Or read this <a href='https://docs.google.com/document/d/1GK-Le5b3U2VD1PaRaEg8irbJPNMVOOpfO2cxYw5Hj2E/edit' target='_blank'>texting guide</a> to know more how to reach other volunteers by texting.
    br
    h3 <strong>Step 1</strong>: You can <a href='http://organize.berniesanders.com'>call other volunteers</a> to have them go to a phonebank OR <a href='https://go.berniesanders.com/page/content/phonebank' target='blank'> call voters from early states</a>.
    br
    h3 <strong>Step 2</strong>: Report your calls/texts. Hover over your profile name (top right), and <a href='javascript: void(null)' onclick="$('#call-in').addClass('show-lightbox'); $(this).closest('li.with-submenu').trigger('mouseout');">click on "Report-In"</a>
